net.sourceforge.gjtapi.raw
Class RawListenerMux

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--net.sourceforge.gjtapi.raw.RawListenerMux
public class RawListenerMux
extends java.lang.Object
implements TelephonyListener

This is a simple RawListener broadcaster that allows multiple remote RawListeners to appear as one to the RawProvider. This simplifies RawProvider construction since they now only have to worry about holding onto one RawListener, not a set. Creation date: (2000-04-26 15:43:02)
